From 3546a410801ae2aa85d52cf43a4eb4ec8211c1ec Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 21:20:47 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Mark external links as such on home page

